lake shore drive ( colloquially referred to as the outer drive , but also sometimes as the drive or lsd ) is a mostly freeway - standard expressway running parallel with and alongside the shoreline of lake michigan through chicago , illinois , usa. except for the portion north of foster avenue ( 5200 north ) , lake shore drive is designated as part of u.s. highway 41 .

hotel : opened in 1920 , the 535-room drake hotel offers gorgeous views of this city 's lake shore drive

